overview: Phillip Riback is large fanatic of Formula 1 as well as GT1, and can be unreservedly declared that he’s a automobile lover. Some people would even say a auto freak, however honestly, that is certainly merely the polite way of saying Phillip Riback is a auto nuts…He’s a fancy car fan, that loves driving!!! Phillip Riback has been engaged in the Automobile field since this individual was 15 years old
